  "description": "<p>🔥[$11/HR]| Perm Part - Time E-Comm Packer | 🔥</p><p><strong>Location 1: Changi Airport Terminal 3 </strong></p><p>Working Day: Monday to Sunday (5 days per week - 4 weekdays & 1 weekend)</p><p>Working Hours: 10am to 6pm*</p><p>Must be able to work on Weekdays, Weekend and Public Holidays</p><p><strong>Location 2: Sin Ming Road (Upper Thomson)</strong></p><p>Working Day: Monday to Friday (5 days per week)*</p><p>Working Hours: 10am to 3pm*</p><p>Able to work on Weekend and Public Holidays when required</p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p>Able to commence work within short notice<br />Must be 16 years old and above<br />Physically fit</p><p><strong>Job Duties</strong></p><p>Ensure that orders picked and packed are accurate, complete, and free from errors. </p><p>Verify customer information and shipping addresses.</p><p>Ensure all packages are well packed to prevent damages.</p><p>Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned. </p><p><strong>Hourly Rate: Weekdays S$11 per hour; Weekends S$12 per hour and Public Holiday S$15 per hour</strong></p><p>Interested applicants, please send your following particulars to WhatsApp 8641 1309 </p><p>1. Name:</p><p>2. Nationality</p><p>3. Contact Number:</p><p>4. Residential Area:</p><p>5. Able to commence work on:</p><p>6. Commitment period:<br /><br />7. Work Location: 1 or 2</p>",
